Used to come here on half days when I was in middle school. My favorite was the fries yumm. Usually took 10 minutes for them to make it but they served them hot and delicious. I remember the owner would kick you out if you brought in a drink purchased from somewhere else. I guess it makes sense but he used to single you out in front of everyone. I mean come on, we were middle school kids! Good thing it never happened to me, I just observed
